        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/xavier_lavoipierre/{size}/1432_2.png",
        "created_at": "2017-04-04T15:46:43.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>By the way, for rentals you can also try Napa Cycle Sport: <a href=\"http://www.napacyclesport.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">http://www.napacyclesport.com</a></p>\n<p>I go to their Sonoma store, Sonoma Valley Cyclery, but I think the Napa store also has a full lineup of rental bikes, from hybrids to performance bikes.</p>",
